longBusinessSummary: European Electric Metals Inc. engages in the acquisition and exploration of natural resource properties. It has an option to acquire 100% interest in the Borba 2 copper project located in Portugal. The company was formerly known as Tirex Resources Ltd. and changed its name to European Electric Metals Inc. in January 2018. European Electric Metals Inc. was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
